      "text": [
        "٢٢٠. وَقَالَ (عليه ‏السلام): لَيْسَ مِنَ الْعَدْلِ الْقَضَاءُ عَلَى الثِّقَةِ بِالظَّنِّ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.sayed-ali-raza": [
          "220. Amīr al-mu’minīn, peace be upon him, said: There is no justice in passing a verdict by relying on probability."
        ]
